title: 820-00165 wont start
message:
Try first to start in SMC bypass mode.

Do you get PM_SLP_SUS_L and 3V3_SUS?
What about PM_RSMRST_L, PM_PWRBTN_L, PM_BATLOW_L?
Check if all 4 RTC signals are good.

title: 820-00165 wont start
message:
That "audio cable" (LIO flex) has a lot of connections, including some power rails , SMC_LID, SYS_ONEWIRE, USB.
Be sure to use proper LIO flex/board for your machine.
Also use Magsafe 2 charger; do NOT use 1-->2 adapter.

Posta again basic voltages and signals w/o LIO flex connected.
You must get it working w/o the flex and then deal with LIO issue...
